node-1746512182699.name: SQL_DimVacuna
node-1746512182699.sqlQuery:
SELECT 
  1 as idVacuna, 'Pentavalente' as Nombre, 'Combinada' as tipoBiologico
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  2 as idVacuna, 'BCG' as Nombre, 'Bacteriana' as tipoBiologico
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  3 as idVacuna, 'Hepatitis B' as Nombre, 'Viral' as tipoBiologico
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  4 as idVacuna, 'Rotavirus' as Nombre, 'Viral' as tipoBiologico
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  5 as idVacuna, 'Antipolio' as Nombre, 'Viral' as tipoBiologico
